"`the image below <ImplementTransStMachine>` below, the state is changed "
"from **``state2``** to **``state3``** (and the current handler is changed "
"from **``state2_handler``** to **``state3_handler``**). The next time "
"**``main_handler``** receives an event, it will be processed by "
"**``state3_handler``**."
